        h2.bullet Having empathy for those you make things with
        ul.headroom
          li Documentation
          li Testing
          li On Boarding (First day / week / month)
          li Be a good ally
          li LISTEN TO THEM

      section
        h2.bullet Having empathy for yourself
        ul.headroom
          li Set healthy boundaries
          li Listen to your body
          li Be aware of impostor syndrome
          li LISTEN TO YOURSELF

